				<p>Tito Kayak hangs a protest banner on a billboard just outside Vega Baja, Puerto Rico, on March 9th, 2018. The banner reads, “We need electricity now! Damn, Damn, Damn!” Kayak prides himself in his unique style of activism that some consider reckless. <br><small>Photo: Rob Gourley</small></p>
