				<p>A framed portrait of Tito Kayak hangs inside one of the church buildings, alongside a portrait of the church’s late priest. Kayak jokes that he does not recognize himself since he appears so young in the portrait. <br><small>Photo: Kaitlin Harlow</small></p>
