				<p>Luisa M. Pérez asked Kayak to take a picture with her after the service. A member of the same church, Pérez expressed admiration for Kayak’s work: “I know Tito from the news, from the events, from the struggle, from the good that he does for Puerto Rico. There are many people that haven’t had help… he is one of the people, the heroes, who has collaborated with the people that the government has forgotten.”<br><small>Photo: Kaitlin Harlow</small></p>
